cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new approach for learning implicit generative models through moment matching. The use of pretrained ConvNets also suggests that it may belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning techniques, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the sub-category of cs.GR (Graphics) due to its focus on style transfer and super-resolution.
